<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000066> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "occurs in"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000066> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "b occurs in c =Def b is a process or a process boundary & c is a material entity or site & there exists a spatiotemporal region r & b occupies spatiotemporal region r & for all time t, if b exists at t then c exists at t & there exist spatial regions s and s' where b spatially projects onto s at t & c occupies spatial region s' at t & s is a continuant part of s' at t"@en .
