_:genid80 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#allValuesFrom> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019> .
_:genid80 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> .
_:genid80 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "quality"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "(Elucidation) A quality is a specifically dependent continuant that, in contrast to roles and dispositions, does not require any further process in order to be realized"@en .
# 
# http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000020
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000020> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000020> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002> .
