# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020117
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020117> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020117> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aggregate state solid"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020117> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A state where the bonds between entities transmit shear forces."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020118
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020118> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020118> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aggregate state liquid"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020118> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A state where the bonds of the entities transmit no shear force."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020119
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020119> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020119> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aggregate state gaseous"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020119> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A state where the entities have no bonding."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020120
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020120> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020120> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aggregate state plasma"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020120> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An aggregate state where the entities are atom nuclei and have no bonds."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020121
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020121> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020121> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aggregate state atom gas"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020121> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A gaseous state where the gas entities are atoms."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020122
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020122> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020122> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aggregate state supercritical fluid"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020122> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A state with strong bindings between entities that do not transmit shear force."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020123
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020123> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020123> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aggregate state mesomorphic"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020123> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A state where some bonds transmit shear stresses and some do not."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020124
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020124> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020124> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aggregate state suprafluid"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020124> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A state with frictionless binding that transmits no shear force between entities."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020125
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020125> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020125> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aggregate state suprasolid"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020125> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A state that exhibits suprafluid and solid properties."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020217
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020217> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020217> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "short range order"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020217> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "periodic arrangement of structural features up to a few entities"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020218
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020218> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020218> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "medium range order"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020218> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "periodic arrangement of structural features of many entities"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020219
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020219> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020219> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "long range order"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020219> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "periodic arrangement of structural features of virtually all entities"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020242
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020242> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020242> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "no range order"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020242> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "no periodic arrangement of structural features of entites"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040128
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040128> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
