<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040128> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "https://www.gs1.org/standards/id-keys/gln" .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040128> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GS1 GLN Specifications"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040128> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "identification scheme that specifies constraints on the structure of a GLN (global location number)" .
